{"tid":304668,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人睇左點五步？","createTime":"2017-07-01T05:29:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T12:16:34.000Z","uid":121744,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3227f34ab7b1838428d1a32d98cef68dd3be32fe","tid":304668,"uid":121744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T05:29:41.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完，又幾好睇。<br />\n<br />\n套戲都幾近似十年，只不過冇咁直接，用左個真人真事去帶出政治現況。<br />\n我自己覺得其實主角個兄弟隠喻緊英國，一路佢兄弟都係佢嘅大樹，而校長要主角唔好縮係英國後邊，要靠自己踏出一步，唔理輸贏都好，最緊要勇敢。<br />\n<br />\n其實姐係叫香港人乜都唔好靠，靠自己最實際。<br />\n<br />\n大家又覺得套戲點？"},{"pid":"f328847140aa7ae236a0289ce0b9ba5bd4bd26cf","tid":304668,"uid":121744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T06:46:25.000Z","msg":"冇人睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"a4126d68f46c41dd56eca143887d60f1b8d2428b","tid":304668,"uid":17506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T07:57:32.000Z","msg":"套野上完好耐,要睇去返高登先見到d人點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[港產片] 《點五步》討論區<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message=6503443&amp;page=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DVI%26message%3D6503443%26page%3D1&d=y7gdkFo918GblnQd%2F2QIJleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=ee0ac0ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message=6503443&amp;page=1</a>"},{"pid":"172aebc27c43372b09721ba9e055df95b5d9b1f4","tid":304668,"uid":22645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"套戲個idea唔錯但係導演嘅功力比較嫩"},{"pid":"8f89826f74d9d882515969a8d9da2d61db526105","tid":304668,"uid":121744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套野上完好耐,要睇去返高登先見到d人點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[港產片] 《點五步》討論區<br />\n<a href=\"http://forum.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=VI&amp;message